Class HemfDraw.EmfPolygon

  • java.lang.Object

    public static class HemfDraw.EmfPolygon
extends HwmfDraw.WmfPolygon
implements HemfRecord
    The EMR_POLYGON record specifies a polygon consisting of two or more vertexes connected by straight lines.(EMR_POLYGON记录指定由两个或多个由直线连接的顶点组成的多边形。)
